channel.title: Simple Question, I Need A Simple Answer
channel.description: Okay, ive gotten my 317 and 562 working fine, other people around the world could connect to it, all of a sudden school came back and i never had them online ever since, now i have the time to make another server, this time ive chosen a 508. i have everything working, 43594 is working, i check on canyouseeme.org i have my no-ip duc v3.0.4 running with my no-ip running. i have my server on, and i changed the client ip from 127.0.0.1 to my no-ip. its was working with 127.0.0.1 now it wont work with my no-ip. ive extracted the cache and put it in my C: drive, and it still wont work, any ideas what im doing wrong?
